          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " at Sport Motors on March 3. Two men showed up at the dealership and asked to see the M4, then wanted the sales rep to turn on the engine so they could hear it at idle. That’s when they asked to talk in private inside the car and the dealership employee figured they were calling their father to talk about a possible purchase.",
